# BREADTH (Quotation) — Wave 2, the twelfth doctype (docs/plans/2026-07-20-breadth-campaign-past-
# 120.md), and the FIRST DYNAMIC-PARTY doctype landed — the judgment call of Wave 2. Quotation
# carries no static header-level "customer" field at all, only a Dynamic Link pair
# (quotation_to + party_name); party_field=None follows Material Request's None-precedent rather
# than forcing the dynamic field into a slot built for a single static fieldname (see erpnext.py's
# SUPPORTED_DOCTYPES comment block for the full source-cited finding). This forces the FIFTH
# _list_fields branch (party_field=None with status AND grand_total both present — a combination
# no prior doctype exercised): TestQuotationListTier proves the tool layer threads the new branch
# unchanged (test_erpnext.py's TestList already pins the client-level field-set shape). The
# submit/cancel TRANSPORT itself is mechanically ordinary (run_method, like every doctype but
# Journal Entry) — TestQuotationGovernedRoundTrip proves the generated mechanical wiring holds end
# to end for a twelfth doctype. Quotation's own landing also repoints two long-standing exemplars
# (TestUnsupportedDoctypeDenied, TestCascadeCancel, below) off itself onto "Transaction Deletion
# Record" — a REFUSE doctype that will never land, closing the repoint churn for good.
# ============================================================================================

class TestQuotationListTier(unittest.TestCase):
    """The ONE genuinely new branch Quotation forces (erpnext.py's SUPPORTED_DOCTYPES/
    _list_fields docstrings have the full source-cited finding): party_field=None (a Dynamic Link
    pair, not an absent/self-clearing party) combined with status AND grand_total BOTH present —
    a combination no prior doctype exercised (Journal Entry drops both; Material Request keeps
    status only; Stock Entry drops both). These are dispatch-level pins (test_erpnext.py's TestList
    already pins the client-level field-set shape); this class proves the tool layer threads the
    same config through unchanged."""

