# dossier's own §11 claim ("status field defaults to Planned") is narrowed rather than rejected:
# confirmed absent from the schema (no "default" key on the status field) and from a full-file
# grep (no code path anywhere ever writes "Planned" — only on_discard writes "Cancelled", and that
