# all (the THIRD doctype after Cost Center Allocation/Supplier Scorecard Period) — a governed
# cancel through this broker changes docstatus only. CASCADE: one real external Link (Master
# Production Schedule.sales_forecast) whose own doctype can never reach docstatus=1
# (is_submittable is None/falsy) — neither a true cascade leaf nor a live external edge.
