        # plan_cancel's projected_reversal comes from get_gl_entries — a REAL, safe bench read
        # (never make_gl_entries), which correctly comes back empty for Sales Forecast (no GL row
        # was ever written under this voucher_type, in either direction — neither on_submit nor
