# BREADTH (Bank Guarantee) — Wave 5, the thirty-fourth doctype and second row (docs/plans/
# 2026-07-20-breadth-campaign-past-120.md; dossier at docs/plans/dossiers/bank_guarantee.md).
# party_field=None — but a genuine DUAL CONDITIONAL customer/supplier pair (never "no party
# concept at all"): both real, static header Link fields, populated per bg_type/reference_doctype
# (client-side only, bank_guarantee.js:36-42) — the Blanket Order precedent. status CONFIRMED
# ABSENT (docstatus only); grand_total also CONFIRMED ABSENT (amount is the sole in_list_view
# Currency field, the aggregate substitute). date_field="start_date" — REJOINS Supplier Scorecard
# Period's own SEVENTH date-fieldname pattern, the second doctype on it, not a new one; its own
# sibling end_date is a genuine dossier gap (client-JS-derived only, never server-computed,
# confirmed absent from bank_guarantee.py entirely). company CONFIRMED ABSENT — the SIXTH
# companyless doctype after Packing Slip/Supplier Scorecard Period/Shipment/Project Update/Asset
# Maintenance Log. Ledger preview UNCALLABLE (bare Document, the simplest MRO in the category).
# submit_via="run_method" — A DOSSIER CORRECTION: the dossier claimed client_rpc citing "an
# on_submit override", but on_submit is a HOOK method, never a def submit(self)/def cancel(self)
# override (confirmed absent by a full 74-line read of bank_guarantee.py); SUBMIT_VIA_CLIENT_RPC
# stays pinned to exactly Journal Entry/Stock Reconciliation. on_submit is a fully deterministic
# doomed-submit gate off three field-presence checks (bank_guarantee_number, name_of_beneficiary,
# bank), each in strict source order, each stopping the check at the first failure; when all
# three pass, submit succeeds with NO further side effect of any kind — the plainest
# "doomed-or-nothing" submit story this campaign has found. on_cancel is CONFIRMED ABSENT
# ENTIRELY, but with nothing for it to reverse either. Cascade LEAF. One read-only whitelisted
# callable (get_voucher_details).
# ============================================================================================

