# directions) writes a status value directly onto every referenced Payment Request/Payment Entry
# via raw frappe.db.set_value — cancel writes "Initiated" UNCONDITIONALLY, a real regression risk
# for a Payment Request whose own status has since moved past that. Cascade: genuinely NOT A LEAF
# — three real incoming submittable edges (Journal Entry/Payment Entry/Payment Request) — joining
# Delivery Trip (not the first) as a real TARGET with real dependents, here with three edges
