# ============================================================================================
# BREADTH (Timesheet) — a Sonnet landing agent off the pre-verification addendum
# (docs/plans/dossiers/timesheet.verify.md, 2026-07-21), the forty-second supported doctype.
# party_field="customer" — a plain, singular, header-level Link, the simple shape for once.
# submit_via="run_method" — the dossier's own "client_rpc" conclusion was WRONG (Timesheet's
# on_submit is an ordinary throwing hook, a 25-def class body with zero submit/cancel overrides).
# status PRESENT — set_status() is THREE SEQUENTIAL UNCONDITIONAL ifs, never if/elif: a truthy
# sales_invoice always wins "Completed" last, overriding a per_billed>=100 "Billed" result.
# grand_total ABSENT, no substitute. company PRESENT BUT OPTIONAL — the FOURTH such row (after
# Purchase Invoice/Quality Inspection/Asset Value Adjustment); the 0fdf91d guard already covers
# it, so NOT companyless-tallied. date_field="start_date" — joins the existing exclusivity set as
# its THIRD member. Ledger preview UNCALLABLE (skip tuple 26th member). THE SECOND WRITER: a
# Sales Invoice's own submit OR cancel can rewrite this Timesheet's status/billing fields via a
# raw whole-document db_update_all(), zero validate()/hooks/permission re-check. Cascade: NOT a
# leaf — the campaign's first confirmed INCOMING child-table Link (Sales Invoice Timesheet.
# time_sheet).
# ============================================================================================

