# ============================================================================================
# BREADTH (Pick List) — a Sonnet landing agent off the pre-verification addendum
# (docs/plans/dossiers/pick_list.verify.md, 2026-07-21), the forty-fourth supported doctype.
# party_field="customer" — a plain, always-real header Link (depends_on is a pure Desk-form
# display directive, never a data-model condition). status PRESENT (hidden:1, reqd:1, 6 options)
# but grand_total ABSENT with no substitute. DATELESS — the FOURTH NO_DATE_FIELD member. company
# reqd=1 — NOT companyless, standard wrong-books belt applies. THE CASCADE QUESTION (the row's
# decisive fact — both the dossier and the addendum concluded LEAF and were WRONG): Delivery Note
# and Sales Invoice are BOTH is_submittable=1; their own child tables carry real Link fields to
# Pick List (against_pick_list) — frappe's own linked_with.py resolves a child-table hit back to
# its submittable PARENT, exactly the mechanism Timesheet's own landing already proved. Stock
# Entry.pick_list is a THIRD, simpler, direct header-level Link on submittable Stock Entry. Pick
# List is NOT a cascade leaf on three independent counts. Ledger preview UNCALLABLE (skip tuple
# 28th member, MRO 4-deep). THE SUBMIT-THROW SURFACE IS 12 SITES, NOT 2: 4 deterministic-from-
# draft + 8 cross-document/live-state, staying prose. THE TWO-JAW TRAP: on_update_after_submit
# throws if has_reserved_stock() (100% draft-deterministic) but on_cancel never throws and
# preserves Serial and Batch Bundle/Stock Reservation Entry/Delivery Note — can't edit once
# reserved, CAN cancel-and-orphan. THE RESERVATION MACHINERY: a multi-hop delegation through
# Sales Order's own method chain (shared with Purchase Receipt today) — a FOURTH cross-document
# mutation honesty grade, nothing granted.
# ============================================================================================

