# ============================================================================================
# BREADTH (Production Plan) — the forty-eighth doctype (docs/plans/dossiers/production_plan.md +
# production_plan.verify.md, unusually strong: it re-verified every dossier line cite). party_
# field=None (customer is a conditional UI filter, never a GL party). status PRESENT (8 options
# incl. Closed/Material Requested) but NOT in_list_view; grand_total ABSENT, no substitute.
# date_field="posting_date" — a plain Date among 5, rejoins the large existing set. Ledger preview
# UNCALLABLE (bare Document, no make_gl_entries anywhere) — skip tuple 29th member. GENUINELY NOT
# A LEAF: three real incoming edges (Work Order's own direct header Link; Purchase Order Item's/
# Material Request Item's own child-table Links resolving to submittable parents) — the dossier's
# own "leaf" claim overturned. THE CANCEL-ORDERING WRINKLE: on_cancel runs BEFORE
# check_no_back_links_exist — this broker's own blast-radius gate refuses first. TWO AUTO-SUBMIT
# CHANNELS: Material Request via a caller-supplied non-persisted flag (prose); Stock Reservation
# Entry, UNCONDITIONAL once the real reserve_stock field is set — the dossier's own
# "auto-submitted: NO" claim overturned. THE FORWARD CHECK: reserve_stock propagates onto every
# Work Order this plan creates — Work Order's OWN landing never discloses this channel, a
# CONFIRMED RETROACTIVE GAP reported here. company PRESENT AND reqd:1. NOT in
# period_closing_doctypes — broker equal-or-stricter, the standing posture.
# ============================================================================================

